1. Two-way mobile messaging is the wave of the future for customer service because:
Solution : B. It's the way most customers communicate in their own lives

2. A benefit of two-way messaging for your business is:
Solution : D. Both A and B

3. Service Cloud Messaging is leading the way to two-way customer service messaging with:
Solution : A. Two-way messaging using a company's existing 1-800 number
